data.description:
Experience the allure of this stunning ranch home situated on a corner lot, perfect for enjoying summer days by the newly installed windows overlooking the pool with loved ones. This home boasts 4 bedrooms and 3 baths, along with an additional non-conforming fifth bedroom. Relish the comfort of new plank flooring and updated fixtures throughout the entire home.

The delightful kitchen is furnished with a bar, freshly painted cabinets, a pantry, and all appliances included. The master bedroom suite features a walk-in closet and a private bathroom. A spacious second bedroom also offers a walk-in closet. The lower level is refined with a fourth bedroom, walk-in closet, and a fifth non-conforming room, excellent for a second office or exercise space.

Enjoy the extensive family room, additional storage room, and a 16X6 safe room, offering ample space for relaxation and security. The backyard beckons with a new pergola, deck surrounding the pool, and an expansive patio, ideal for summer gatherings. The third-car driveway, suitable for additional vehicles or an RV, is enclosed by a privacy fence.

Additional conveniences include a storage shed and a cozy covered front porch. Benefit from seamless access to the I-49 interstate and the walking distance to restaurants, a gas station, a health clinic, a salon, a boutique, a bank, and a park.
